response.original_title: The Jezabels: Live at the Hordern Pavilion
response.overview: The Jezabels release a DVD of their live performance on stage at the Hordern Pavillion in Sydney during their Prisoner album launch.  Tracklist 01. Endless Summer 02. Easy To Love 03. Rosebud 04. City Girl 05. Mace Spray 06. Nobody Nowhere 07. Horsehead 08. Long Highway 09. Trycolour 10. A Little Piece 11. Deep Wide Ocean 12. Dark Storm 13. Peace Of Mind 14. Hurt Me
response.title: The Jezabels: Live at the Hordern Pavilion
